Photo by Forex Trading Strategies on August 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'If you open a long position with a trailing stop, the stop will automatically follow the price as it moves upwards Lo Position Initial Stop-Loss Stop'.
Photo by Forex Trading Strategies on August 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'New Stop-Loss Level, stays the same unless price moves up Stop-Loss Stop InitialStop-Loss Stop-Loss'.

Photo by Forex Trading Strategies on August 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Trailing stops will move up as the price moves, but when the price reverses, the stop will remain stationary and close the trade out if it's touched. The Stop-Loss is just updated on new price highs New Stop-Loss InitiaS-Los Stop-Loss'.

Photo by Forex Trading Strategies on August 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Trailing stops are a great way to let profitable positions run and simultaneously negate the possibility of losing all of your gains to a reversal. Position Closed at Trailing Stop Loss Initial Stop-Loss'.
